ss=\"mtk17\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk4\">div</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"mtk17\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mtk4\">div</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">class</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#39;parent1&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk14\">/</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre>\n<p><img src=\"/blogs/interview-css/css_2_pic_2.jpg#pic_center\" alt=\"pic_2\"></p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li><strong>清除内部浮动</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<p>触发父元素的 BFC 属性，使子元素都处在父元素的同一个 BFC 区域之内，实现清除浮动。</p>\n<p><img src=\"/blogs/interview-css/css_2_pic_3.jpg#pic_center\" alt=\"pic_3\"></p>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li><strong>BFC 的区域不会与 float box 重叠</strong></li>\n</ol>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"74227684958162060000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster copyToaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text copyToasterText\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"copy successfully!\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"5000\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`<style>\n  .parent {\n    background-color: #f0f0f0;\n  }\n  .bfc {\n    overflow: hidden; /*触发 BFC，不影响外部元素*/\n  }\n  .child1 {\n    float: left;\n    width: 100px;\n    height: 100px;\n    background-color: red;\n  }\n  .child2 {\n    width: 300px;\n    height: 100px;\n    background-color: blue;\n  }\n</style>\n\n<div class='parent'>\n  <div class='bfc'>\n    <div class='child1'></div>\n  </div>\n  <div class='child2'></div>\n</div>`, `74227684958162060000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button copyButton\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                copy<svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\"